Gaupol 0.12
===========

 [D] Add a capitalization task to the text correction assistant
 [D] Add "All supported files" filter to the open dialog
 [D] Fix error saving after splitting project (#10041)
 [D] Fix NameErrors with lambda functions (#10034)
 [D] Fix error opening SubRip file if the first line is blank (#10054)
 [D] Fix markup tooltip hack to work with (Py)GTK 2.12
 [D] Remove license page from the Windows installer
 [D] Include iso-codes with the Windows installer


Gaupol 0.13
===========

 * Migrate to (Py)GTK 2.12
    - gtk.AboutDialog: "name" replaced with "program-name"
    - gtk.Builder: Build an interface from an XML UI definition
    - gtk.RecentAction: New class for recent-files menu items
    - gtk.Tooltip: New API that allows complex tooltips
    - Fix changed text assistant backwards movement behaviour


Gaupol 1.0
==========

 * Plugin system (see gedit for interfaces)
    - gaupol.gtk.Plugin
    - gaupol.gtk.PluginManager
    - Dialog or a page in the preferences dialog
 * Side and bottom panes?
 * Allow arbitrary attributes on gaupol.Subtitle?
 * Allow arbitrary columns in gaupol.gtk.View?
 * Example plugin: Bookmarks?


